    "title": [
      "[Noralgar Hollow, Water Reeds]"
    ],
    "description": [
      "The path curves around the boggy edge of Moonlight Pool, its edge marked by tall water reeds.  Bull frogs and lesser amphibians sing a mixed chorus from the protection of the grasses.  Cottages built along the curved bank sit contemplating the mirror-like surface of the water, dotted intermittently with loons swimming at the far end."
    ],
